release_note: Animated filter parameters: We ve added silky smoothness to our 150 filters. Controls now slide elegantly from one tap to the next. Want to animate your NFTs to a totally new vibe Tap a filter multiple times to fluidly flip between random unique looks. New tessellation sets: GeoTile PolyTile and GlowTile have been updated with 19 new shapely tessellation parameters. We at Generate have essentially conquered geometry. New SlowTile filter: Time angles and spectrum meld together for macro dosed fun in this new tessellation motion combo filter. Pro tip: This effect needs motion to use it with a still image input add some wiggle with the Wobbler filter. New presets: We created a fresh set of preset combos to highlight our new filters including Alternet CDROM Closer and InABand. As well as their initial look tap on these presets again to mix them up. Each will produce a practically infinite variety of smooth styles for cooler creative.

As artists ourselves we know how crucial your creative tools are. That s why we re dropping one of our most substantial releases ever so that you can better create and sell your art. GENERATE PRO Now includes: All 150 filters access to our professional artist network exclusive event invites and opportunities to sell your work. NFT Ready Non Fungible Tokens have created a quantum shift in the art world so Generate now includes NFT focused aesthetics layering and output functionality. UI OVERHAUL Our fully revamped interface helps you get down to the business of creating art faster easier and simpler than ever before. LAYERING Our brand new Layering section lets you integrate multiple photos and videos to build customized filters that you can save. HIGH RESOLUTION We ve drastically increased our output fidelity so your work can be displayed in high quality across social media and in NFT galleries. NEW FILTERS AND CATEGORIES Explore new creative territory with inspiring new Chroma and Pattern filters. Our filter category system has also been overhauled so you can more quickly and intuitively create NFT worthy artworks. BUG FIXES We have tackled usability issues across our entire workflow. For questions comments or anything else you can reach us at info generateapp.com

Introducing the Generate Activity screen and new ways to share the Generate creative community. The Activity section is a new central hub for social interactions receiving important messages and interactions between community members. We ve also added a new addition to your filter collection Light Speed. Share your love for Generate creativity from the Gallery. Star your favs and get notified when others favorite yours. We ve added the ability to share Gallery posts to SMS email Facebook and Twitter so friends can see and share the best media made with Generate. After hearing requests for better community engagement the new Activity and Gallery are an easy and fun way to engage with images and videos. Plus now Generate PRO users can share longer videos to Generate showcasing even more excellent content in the Gallery.

Introducing video looping in Generate. After receiving much feedback from the community now videos will continue to play as you re applying effects. This gives you more freedom for video editing creativity. We ve also made updates to our Facebook sign up and log in process. For new users we ve added a walk through process that makes it easier to get started with Generate. You ll also find two new filters in our store get your hands on PINK and Color to add incredible highlights to your media.

The latest version of Generate introduces Adobe Creative Cloud sharing important bug fixes and new filters. Introducing Adobe Creative Cloud on Generate. Now you can share your Generate content to the cloud for easier media management and editing using Adobe s Creative Cloud. This exciting new feature is just the beginning of a larger Adobe Creative Cloud integration making it better than ever to use Generate to create images and videos. We ve also loaded this release with important bug fixes. We ve resolved saving a video made with an imported image and fixed launch crashes on ios 9 devices. We ve also fixed the ability to delete profile posts on devices using ios 9 and built better support for time based filters like FADED which require more intensive processing. Plus you can find our newest filter VHS 01 available in the in app store.

Generate is happy to release a new version including updates for iOS 9 support and better handling for library image editing in response to community feedback. Many thanks to everyone who took the time to report and provide feedback on these issues. Also introducing a new social views count in the Curated Gallery and two incredible new filters Melt and Light Leak available from our in app store.

This version addresses a number of stability issues and also contains a number of bug fixes. We re also very excited to release another new free filter Tile that lets you stack and duplicate images to create a 4 up look. Thanks to our creative community for helping us address these! Please email support generateapp.com with any questions and comments. Bug Fixes Crash issues on launch of the app and when using with different filters Audio reactivity issues when using different filters Fixed bugs related to saving library video and stills Compatibility: This app is optimized for iPhone 5 iPhone 6 and iPad Air and later. It is compatible with earlier versions of iPhone iPad and iPod Touch.

Generate adds new filters to the carousel including Pop and Vid Mix. You can also find the new filters Wavy and Trails in the in app store. There are a number of bug fixes related to performance issues as well as the addition of a change username function located in the profile settings.

Generate introduces filter management settings. Rearrange and turn filters on and off using the new filter Settings. Our new general Settings located in your Profile lets you get help reset your password invite friends to Generate rate and report problems. With the addition of the new free filter FADED Generate is all set for summer fun!

Generate is excited to introduce five incredible new filters: Chroma Twitch RGB Reflect and Diamond. Find them in our in app store. Now you can delete Generates from your profile. Plus we ve integrated better permissions requests for new users as well as fixed critical bugs to importing media.

In the latest version of Generate we ve redesigned the login and signup process as well as our in app store and profile. This improves the overall experience and navigating the interface as a new user. There are several important bug fixes to visual projection and image quality for PRO users.

In the latest release Generate has made several updates to the graphical interface. This includes an updated share screen and new buttons and text that make it easier to navigate with a simplified design approach. We have also updated our backend structure allowing for improvements to the systems management.

Introducing landscape mode for capturing videos and images. Now you can record in either square or landscape formats using the drop down menu at the top of the camera interface. The latest release also includes important bug fixes to audio reactivity using the microphone.

Introducing landscape mode for capturing videos and images. Now you can record in either square or landscape formats using the drop down menu at the top of the camera interface. The latest release also includes important bug fixes to audio reactivity using the microphone.

This release includes an important fix for saving media. We want to thank our community for giving us their valuable feedback on this issue and their help in its resolution. Anyone who experienced problems saving media should download this release. We ve also fixed some bugs related to password retrieval and UI updates within the Profile.

This release features the inclusion of Generate Pro in the Generate store and in app purchasing functionality. Supporting this we have implemented an overhaul of our applications backend to provide security and performance updates. Navigation issues have been addressed by the replacement of several buttons to help guide users in entering and exiting the tool. Various bug fixes and UI UX improvements have been implemented throughout the application including an optimized onboarding process removing the walkthrough in favour of several in app tooltips and a new launch image with animated logo.

New look! New filters! Generate has an updated look and feel plus a brand new in app store. And we ve created three new filters you ll love: Dilation Swirl Contrast. Select a track from your library and choose the start point. The image or video in Generate will react live to the audio in the track. You may have noticed that the last version of Generate addressed a ton of feedback we have gotten from users with improved media quality reworked audio reactivity Facebook sign up a new filter and more. This week we have even more updates to share with you. In addition to releasing Versions 1.3.1 we have been work hard on Generate Pro where you can make hi res images and video and record unlimited video. The Pro version also has projection capabilities with many more features to come The Pro version is available on an invite only basis at bit.ly generate pro. Saving To save images and videos click on the large red capture button in the bottom centre of the screen. This button is also used to toggle between still images and video. Feed and Share screens Feed now includes video New curated feed to replace the all feed Optional sharing to generate GUI updates Touch the screen to trigger an autofocus and exposure animation Camera flash animation Bugs and minor updates Fix for mosaic bug it no longer inverts the background colour Fix for rotation bug in certain cases Version 1.3.0 released July 16th Media quality: Higher resolution video 640p and stills 720p Better video compression settings Videos can be created from still images Videos can be up to 7 seconds long Audio reactivity: Filters are much more responsive to the audio signal Filters now react to the audio track in a video Signup: You can now log in or sign up using Facebook You are no longer required to make an account before using Generate Other changes: New filter: Kaleidoscope Additional bug fixes and performance improvements Improved stability for media from camera roll Generate Pro is now available on an invite only basis. Features include: Live projection using Airplay or an adapter cable Unlimited video length Higher resolution video and image output We would like to say thanks for all the support we have received so far. There are Generate users in 132 countries and counting! Don t forget to tag your Generates with generateapp when you share them so we can see what you make. If you have any comments questions or feedback we would love to hear from you. You can reach us at info igenerate.co
